caption:
Have you ever wished that your brows were more like sisters rather than distant cousins? Say no more! We're serving you with the best brow tips EVER, so you can get that symmetrical brow going. 

✨ Let your brows grow out for 4-6 weeks 
✨ Only tweeze strays between your brow and lid 
✨ Start using our Brow and Lash Rejuvenator to strengthen your brows
✨ Don't ignore your natural arch
✨ Trust in the process and be patient

Asymmetrical brows can sometimes require several sessions before being completely transformed. Be patient with your hair!

If you found these tips useful, hit that save button now.
